= ACTIVITES =

ScriptManager  - Tab widget 
    SCRIPTS TAB - saved scripts
    INTENTS TAB - intent library
    FILTERS TAB - filter library

ScriptBuilder   - Wizard walkthrough of creating scripts/intents
    Name        
    Icon        - icon gallery, android.R.drawable and sdcard
    Intent
        Action  Category  Uri 
        Type    Program   Extra

ShortcutMaker





Script is:
    Name
    Icon
    1+ Intents

Intent is:
    Action      VIEW, EDIT, DIAL, CALL, SEND, SENDTO, ANSWER, RUN, PICK_ACTIVITY, SEARCH, WEB_SEARCH
    Category    LAUNCHER, SETTINGS
    Uri         tel: smsto:// mailto:// content:// file:// http:// geo: voicemail: im://
    Type        audio/* video/* text/plain text/html 
    Program     (package,class) com.hlidskialf.android.shortcuts,ScriptBuilder
    Extras      String int long boolean double float short byte 


Filter is:
    Action
    Category
    Uri (type, scheme, authority, path)
    Priority

Builtin Filters:
    SMS Received
    Phone State     (new voicemail, signal strength, call state, traffic)
    Boot 
    Battery Status  
    Gps Location
    Audio Service
    Alarm Manager
    Storage monitor
    Mount service
    Wifi
    Wallpaper
    internal/telephony/gsm/SMSDispatcher?



Builtin Intents:
    Vibrate
    Play media
    Play dtmf
    Wakelock
    Battery status
    Flashlight
    Create notification
    Delayed intent
    System Settings:
        Ringer mode
        Bluetooth On/Discoverable
        GPS
        WIFI
        3G
        Airplane
        Data Roaming
        Autolock
        Sound Effects
        Stay on while plugged in
        12/24hr
        Wifi Available
        Debug
        Set default ringtone/notification
        Set screen brightness
